  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ol><li>Lead, facilitate and mange a team of M & E Department.</li><li>Liaise with project teams to drive initiatives to improve construction work processes.</li><li>Liaise with authorities on incentives and productivity related issues under the guidance of Senior Manager.</li><li>Prepare proposals for submission to authorities</li><li>Prepare progress reports</li><li>Prepare & Submission of RFI/FCR.</li><li>Shop Drawing/Material Review & Submission.</li><li>Attend to all relevant contracts administration and documentation for project.</li><li>To work out cost estimation/ budgetary cost on electrical services</li><li>Liside with suppliers for quotations</li><li>To supervise the overall site works related to M&E service and ensure in line with safety requirements</li><li>To liaise with respective parties on checking of drawings</li><li>Attending to all site meetings with owner, consultants and main-contractors on all matters relating to the project operation and coordination</li></ol>",
